title: Psychobook Games, Tests, Questionnaires, Histories (2016) Gooner
description:
Psychobook Games, Tests, Questionnaires, Histories (2016) (Epub) Gooner

Publisher: Princeton Architectural Press; 01 edition (20 Sept. 2016)
Language: English
ISBN-10: 161689492X
ISBN-13: 978-1616894924

Psychobook takes a subversive, sideways look at psychology and its tools and methods, and contains fascinating content and images. With Psychobook people of all ages can develop their emotional intelligence, discover their imaginations, and delve deeper into their subconscious with interactive quizzes, games, and questionnaires from classics like the Rorshach Inkblot test to surveys remastered and reinvented for a new generation
